208
00:13:39,660 --> 00:13:41,740
Nie, je to moja vina.

209
00:13:41,740 --> 00:13:44,800
Čo hľadáte? Vitamíny?

210
00:13:44,800 --> 00:13:46,280
Koľko Betagenu?

211
00:13:46,280 --> 00:13:47,620
Všetko, čo tam je.

212
00:13:47,620 --> 00:13:49,380
Vezmem aj dezinfekčné prostriedky.

213
00:13:49,380 --> 00:13:51,160
Prepáč.

214
00:14:02,890 --> 00:14:04,970
Sadnite si na chvíľu.

215
00:14:06,660 --> 00:14:08,200
Postarám sa o ňu.

216
00:14:08,200 --> 00:14:09,720
Dobre.

