Je to anestézia.

218
00:14:36,590 --> 00:14:39,390
Bože, tá je tvrdohlavá.

219
00:14:39,390 --> 00:14:42,330
Hovoríte, že sa bojíte ihiel?

220
00:14:42,330 --> 00:14:45,090
Aj napriek tomu, že máte veľké bolesti?

221
00:14:45,090 --> 00:14:47,440
Ani anglicky nevie.

222
00:14:49,320 --> 00:14:52,950
Je to anestézia.

223
00:14:57,080 --> 00:14:59,290
Nechajte ma to urobiť.

224
00:15:02,810 --> 00:15:04,080
Bože.

225
00:15:04,080 --> 00:15:06,750
Nie. Nie anestézia. 

226
00:15:06,750 --> 00:15:08,470
Som tehotná. Anestézia 
